        "Que_18" => [
        "question" => "18. What happens to my answers if I don't qualify for a survey?",
        "answer" => "If you do not qualify for a survey, your responses cannot be utilized in the final research insight, and as a result, they will not be transferred to our clients. Similarly, SJ Panel will not employ or transfer these responses for internal purposes. Since the answers you provided are incomplete or unapproved by our client, they cannot be used for our clients' research and thus you will not receive points when you have not completed the survey."
