        "Que_21" => [
        "question" => "21. What are the benefits of participating in surveys?",
        "answer" => "In addition to earning money, there are other benefits to participating in surveys. For example, you may learn about new products and service developments before they are launched in the market or still in concept stage. Besides earning incentives, you are helping to shape the future of products and services for fellow countrymen and mankind by providing your feedback."
        ],
        "Que_22" => [
        "question" => "22. How do I redeem my SJ points for rewards? ",
        "answer" => 'To redeem your SJ points for rewards, simply log in to your SJ Panel account and go to the "Redeem Points" section. Once there, you can select the desired points amount for redemption, provided your account has reached the minimum threshold of 5000 points.'
